title: Independent candidate Muhammad Sana Ullah Khan Mastikhel NA-91 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Muhammad Sana Ullah Khan Mastikhel has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-91 Bhakkar-I by securing 106,003 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz candidate Abdul Majeed Khan, who bagged 85,429 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 62.93 percent.
